-------------------

We have these way cute, cheesy installation videos you can watch here: http://installationvideos.com

Dust your wall, DO NOT wash with chemicals as this could leave a film on your wall. Soapy water is ok if you feel in is needed. Decals must be applied to a smooth, flat, clean, and dry surface (such as walls, windows, tile, mirrors, doors, etc.). Textured wall do affect install.
